# DIY Apple Wine Recipe

Recipe for simple homemade apple wine made from off-the-shelf apple juice and yeast from Amazon. Based on [Homemade Wine Recipe](https://www.allrecipes.com/recipe/58561/homemade-wine/).

## Ingredients

- 2.5 g [K1-V1116 wine yeast](https://smile.amazon.com/gp/product/B004348K2Y/ref=ppx_yo_dt_b_asin_title_o04_s00?ie=UTF8&psc=1)
- 1.54 L (52 fl. oz) 100% apple juice
- 1.5 cups sugar
- 64 oz growler
- [Airlock](https://smile.amazon.com/gp/product/B00IGXQ5I4/ref=ppx_yo_dt_b_search_asin_title?ie=UTF8&psc=1)

## Directions

0. SANATIZE EVERYTHING AND KEEP IT CLEAN THE WHOLE TIME
1. Activate yeast per packet directions
2. Dissolve sugar in equal parts apple juice on stove
3. Cool juice/sugar mix <= 95 degrees farenheight as to not kill the yeast
4. Add activated yeast to juice/sugar mix
5. Pour leftover juice and juice/sugar/yeast mix into growler, top with airlock
6. Store in a cool, dark place for 4 weeks
